pipeline_summary.name: executive_sales_dashboard
pipeline_summary.description: Sensorgated pipeline that waits for the daily_sales_aggregation DAG, loads the aggregated sales CSV, and generates an executive dashboard.

components.name: Wait for Sales Aggregation
components.description: Monitors the external daily_sales_aggregation DAG and blocks pipeline execution until it completes successfully.

upstream_policy.description: No upstream dependencies; this is the entry point of the pipeline.

components.name: Load Sales CSV
components.description: Loads and validates the aggregated sales CSV data produced by the upstream DAG.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after the wait_for_sales_aggregation sensor succeeds.

components.name: Generate Executive Dashboard
components.description: Creates an executive dashboard with sales metrics and visualizations from the validated sales data.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after load_sales_csv successfully produces validated sales data.

description.default: Sensorgated pipeline that waits for the daily_sales_aggregation DAG, loads the aggregated sales CSV, and generates an executive dashboard.

batch_window.description: Batch window parameter name (e.g., ds, execution_date)

partitioning.description: Data partitioning strategy (e.g., daily, hourly, monthly)

depends_on_past.description: Whether execution depends on previous run success

external_dag_id.description: ID of the external DAG to monitor

external_task_id.description: Specific task within the external DAG to monitor (None means whole DAG)

allowed_states.description: List of states that satisfy the sensor

failed_states.description: List of states that cause the sensor to fail

timeout.description: Maximum time (seconds) to wait for the external DAG

python_callable.description: Python callable that loads and validates the aggregated sales CSV
Python callable that creates the executive dashboard from validated sales data

sources: Aggregated sales CSV files produced by the daily_sales_aggregation DAG

sinks: Email alerts sent via SMTP on task failures
